    <h1>The unrivaled leader in hospitality distribution</h1>


    <p data-redactor-inserted-image="true"><img src="/application/files/3614/8615/4219/CR_screen.png" width="686" height="545" id="image-marker" style="display: block; margin: auto; width: 686px; height: 545px;">  </p><p>SynXis Central Reservations (CR) is the most robust, flexible, easy-to-use rate and inventory management SaaS application. These tools enable hoteliers to support a multitude of rate, inventory and distribution strategies to achieve their business goals.<br>  </p><p><strong>Expand Lifetime Share of Wallet and Grow ADR<br></strong>Leverage powerful revenue management controls to drive a significant increase in ADR.  </p><p><strong>Grow Core Contribution and Brand Loyalty<br></strong>Engage with common customers across brands with deep loyalty integration, and leverage distribution reach to drive adoption and engagement.  </p><p><strong>Unmatched Partner Connectivity and Ease of Integration<br></strong>Experience seamless connectivity to over 120 property management, 7 revenue management, 7 CRM and 18 content management solutions.  </p><p><strong>Rate Parity and Last Room Availability<br></strong>Capture more revenue with real-time rate and inventory information across all channels with integrated reporting tools.  </p><p>SynXis Central Reservations (CR) provides unlimited scalability connecting you to all channels (including GDS, OTAs and Call Center) with a simple user interface and tablet-ready features for managing hotel inventory from anywhere.  </p><p>A powerful pricing engine with sophisticated revenue management controls sets SynXis CR apart from the competition. Even the most complicated rate strategies can be implemented for a single property or across a large chain.  </p><p>Seamless integration between SynXis CR and property systems means cost savings, synchronized data and happy guests.  </p><p><br>  </p><h2>Interested in learning more?  </h2><p style="margin: 20px 0px;" rel="margin: 20px 0px;"><a class="link-button" style="background-color:#e50000; color:#ffffff;" href="/contact/sales-team">REQUEST MORE INFORMATION</a></p><p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;" rel="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><br>  </p>
		</div>
	</div>
